<div class="alert alert-danger">
  <strong><h4>Error!</h4></strong>
  <br>
  <div class="global-err-content">
    <%= detail %>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="err-help">
  If you need more help on this issue, email us at <a href="mailto:support@rockstor.com" target="_blank">support@rockstor.com</a> with the following information:
  <ul>
    <li>The error message: <%= detail %></li>
    <li>A step by step description of the actions leading up to the error.</li>
    <li>Download the tarred and zipped server logs by clicking <a href="/logs/error.tgz" target="_blank">here</a>, and attach it to the email.</li>
  </ul>
</div> <!-- err-help -->

